            . I and the prosecutor were walking arm in arm. I heard the prosecutor say, friend I don't thank you for picking my pocket. I seeing the handkerchief in the prisoner's hand, immediately laid hold of him, and we carried him to the watchhouse.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence.</p>
               <p>I was not near the man. I saw his handkerchief hanging three parts out of his pocket as I was going by.</p>
